WEBVTT

1
00:00:02.266 --> 00:00:04.600
Fu Yuanchuan benar-benar menikahiku.

2
00:00:05.466 --> 00:00:07.366
Rasanya seperti mimpi.

3
00:00:08.300 --> 00:00:11.766
